sql_query.sql: SELECT "accounts"."id", "accounts"."uri" FROM "accounts" INNER JOIN "follows" ON "accounts"."id" = "follows"."account_id" WHERE "follows"."target_account_id" = $1 AND ("accounts"."uri" LIKE 'https://example.org/%' OR "accounts"."uri" = $2) ORDER BY "accounts"."id" ASC LIMIT $3
